      <title>前德意志银行将南非医院连锁业务转向诊断护理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ex-deutsche-bank-pivots-south-african-hospital-chain-to-diagnostic-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着临床入院人数趋于稳定，生命医疗集团控股有限公司 (Life Healthcare Group Holdings Ltd.) 首席执行官彼得沃顿胡德 (Peter Wharton-Hood) 正在将这家南非市值最大的医院连锁店转向诊断和医疗保健服务领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ex-deutsche-bank-pivots-south-african-hospital-chain-to-diagnostic-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:38:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称复星计划通过大宗交易削减 Gland Pharma 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/fosun-is-said-to-plan-block-deals-to-pare-stake-in-gland-pharma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，上海复星医药集团股份有限公司因无法一次性出售其所持有的印度格兰特制药有限公司 (Gland Pharma Ltd.) 股份，正商谈通过大宗交易的方式削减其所持股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/fosun-is-said-to-plan-block-deals-to-pare-stake-in-gland-pharma</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
